  "text": "This study incorporates the product attribute life theory, which predicts that profits will increase as sales increase [CITATION_1] ). The new heifer product attribute is the additional requirement that the heifer's sire EPD accuracy levels must meet minimum accuracy levels. This attribute requirement is recognized in SMS sales brochures by denoting heifers as Tier II compliant. SMS started the Tier II classification in 2008. This classification has potentially created a new value-added product as compared with Tier I heifers.",
